tonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gnr1665702654145.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gnr1665702654145.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gnr1665702654145.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gnr1665702654145\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /dtd\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Compile DTD objects.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__section_w2262ab1b5b1_w2263ab1b5_w2264ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__p_d149003e1_d149004e1_d149005e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/dtd</span> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/inf</span> | <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/war</span>} {<code class=\"ph codeph\">/aft=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">datetime</var>} {<code class=\"ph codeph\">/bef=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">datetime</var>} {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__section_w2265ab1b5b3_w2266ab1b5_w2267ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d357297e82\">\n                  \n Switches\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__d6407e22\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"czj1665702653450.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/czj1665702653450.html\" title=\"Display the information listing plus warning and error messages when compiling.\">/inf</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__d6407e27\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wmw1665702653597.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wmw1665702653597.html\" title=\"Display warning and error messages when compiling.\">/war</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__d6407e32\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ide1665702625805.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ide1665702625805.html\" title=\"Compile objects modified after and/or before the date specified.\">/aft= or /bef=</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__section_w2268ab1b5b5_w2269ab1b5_w2270ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d357297e121\">\n                  \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__p_d149012e1_d149013e1_d149014e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>—model name or search profile to use as selector for the DTDs; if omitted, all DTDs are compiled (after considering any sub-switches).</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__section_w2271ab1b5b7_w2272ab1b5_w2273ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d357297e133\">\n                  \n Use With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__d5931e20\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">ide.exe</span>—Uniface IDE</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__section_w2274ab1b5b9_w2275ab1b5_w2276ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d357297e145\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gnr1665702654145__p_d149024e1_d149025e1_d149026e1\">By default, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/dtd</span> displays error messages but no warning messages. (Compiling interactively displays both error and warning messages by default.) Increase the amount of information displayed by using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/inf</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/war</span> sub-switches.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfc1665702625593.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Compiling from the IDE Command Line</a><p>The IDE command line can be used to compile multiple objects without opening the IDE. It is especially useful for automating compilation by means of batch scripts.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uab1665702654218.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface-Compliant DTDs</a><p>A Document Type Definition (DTD) defines rules for the structure of an XML stream. In Uniface, a DTD is a development object that includes DTD definitions and a default mapping between the XML elements defined by the DTD and Uniface component fields and entities. It can be used to define the rules for the structure of an XML stream that is exchanged between components.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527934\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527934\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/dtd Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /dtd Compile DTD objects. /dtd { /inf | /war } { /aft= datetime } { /bef= datetime } { Model } Switches /inf /war /aft= or /bef= Parameters Model —model name or search profile to use as selector for the DTDs; if omitted, all DTDs are compiled (after considering any sub-switches). Use With ide.exe —Uniface IDE Description By default, /dtd displays error messages but no warning messages. (Compiling interactively displays both error and warning messages by default.) Increase the amount of information displayed by using the /inf , and /war sub-switches. Related Links Compiling from the IDE Command Line The IDE command line can be used to compile multiple objects without opening the IDE. It is especially useful for automating compilation by means of batch scripts. Uniface-Compliant DTDs A Document Type Definition (DTD) defines rules for the structure of an XML stream. In Uniface, a DTD is a development object that includes DTD definitions and a default mapping between the XML elements defined by the DTD and Uniface component fields and entities. It can be used to define the rules for the structure of an XML stream that is exchanged between components. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}